Dear <%= @user.name %>,

Someone has requested to reset your password for your account on Blog. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.

To reset your password, please follow these steps:

1. Click on the following link to begin the password reset process:
  <%= link_to 'reset password', edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>

2. You will be directed to a secure page where you can verify your identity.

3. After verifying your identity, you'll be able to create a new password for your account.

Please note the following:

- This link is temporary and will expire within 24 hours for security reasons.

Thank you for using Blog.